  • 使用Document的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    org.jsoup

    org.jsoup.helper

    HTML document structure nodes.
    org.jsoup.parser
    Contains the HTML parser, tag specifications, and HTML tokeniser.
    org.jsoup.safety
    Contains the jsoup HTML cleaner, and whitelist definitions.
